```plantuml
@startuml OpiumProtocol_opium-protocol-v2

actor User
participant "Core" as Core
participant "SyntheticAggregator" as SyntheticAggregator
participant "OracleAggregator" as OracleAggregator
participant "OpiumProxyFactory" as OpiumProxyFactory
participant "Opium Position Tokens" as PositionTokens
participant "Registry" as Registry
participant "TokenSpender" as TokenSpender

User -> Core: Create Position
Core -> Registry: Get Configurations
Registry --> Core: Return Configurations

activate Core
Core -> SyntheticAggregator: Validate Derivative
SyntheticAggregator --> Core: Return Validation Result

alt Validation Successful
    Core -> OracleAggregator: Fetch Price Data
    OracleAggregator --> Core: Return Price Data

    Core -> OpiumProxyFactory: Deploy Position Tokens
    OpiumProxyFactory --> Core: Return Token Addresses

    Core -> TokenSpender: Transfer Tokens
    TokenSpender --> Core: Confirm Transfer

    Core -> PositionTokens: Issue LONG/SHORT Tokens
    deactivate Core
else Validation Failed
    deactivate Core
    User <-- Core: Return Error
end

@enduml
```